{"tid":1591666,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國際記協譴責《環時》抹黑香港記協","createTime":"2019-09-24T09:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T11:14:54.000Z","uid":212626,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"eeb0fbaf063eb87ca1308cb3aa515ea8b898ba05","tid":1591666,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:01:17.000Z","msg":"...<br />\nThe IFJ said:&quot;<span style=\"color: red;\">We strongly deplore this smear campaign against our affiliate the HKJA</span>. The work of the HKJA is commendable, especially the continued support and campaigning for media safety in the past four months in Hong Kong. <span style=\"color: red;\">We stand in solidarity and support the HKJA</span>. The IFJ was never sort for comment regarding the campaign to have HKJA's membership revoked. The attempts by some to share disinformation are part of a campaign to discredit the work done by HKJA, supported by the IFJ to ensure the safety and security of the media and press freedom in Hong Kong.&quot;<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ifj.org/media-centre/news/detail/category/press-releases/article/hong-kong-ifj-condemns-smear-campaign-to-discredit-hkja.html?fbclid=IwAR348wRaYK4v28KV1XbHT9eueQBd5MGe_aeSYuvqau66ho8BfWjIxH1RhGs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifj.org%2Fmedia-centre%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2Fcategory%2Fpress-releases%2Farticle%2Fhong-kong-ifj-condemns-smear-campaign-to-discredit-hkja.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR348wRaYK4v28KV1XbHT9eueQBd5MGe_aeSYuvqau66ho8BfWjIxH1RhGs&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqL9EqtgOipuK5hw8%2B6jdv%2Bo%3D&h=78107c2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ifj.org/media-centre/news/detail/category/press-releases/article/hong-kong-ifj-condemns-smear-campaign-to-discredit-hkja.html?fbclid=IwAR348wRaYK4v28KV1XbHT9eueQBd5MGe_aeSYuvqau66ho8BfWjIxH1RhGs</a><br />\n<br />\n環時尋日整咗啲咁嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RUS2a2F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRUS2a2F.jpg&h=6d8d09db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e3cf317b6708a22c08e7ad6ba48c80c06b6e03e","tid":1591666,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:03:06.000Z","msg":"聲明寫道：「香港記者協會不但沒有擔當起公正、持平的記者工會的角色，反而處處對立場不同的媒體/記者採取不同的標準，政治立場偏袒，嚴重破壞市民對本港傳媒行業的觀感。作為傳媒工作者一份子，我們發起『記協不代表我』連署行動，收集業界人士的簽名，向記協說不！」<br />\n<br />\n另外，傳媒人士還發起「一人一信」行動，邀請社會各界人士一人一信，去信國際記者聯盟(電子郵箱：ifj@ifj.org)投訴，要求取消香港記協的會員資格。同時，聲明中還列舉了香港記協的五大「受質疑行為」，包括「包庇記者劣行」、「縱容假記者」、「縱容假新聞」、「雙重標準」和「小圈子運作」。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf099226b7b770bd1b0e878b609684b51aabc4f","tid":1591666,"uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:04:06.000Z","msg":"記協代表記者，梗係不代表「我」"},{"pid":"01f1b89658692940442ca2eb805abf6b54342a15","tid":1591666,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:04:47.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n理解大家都好緊張手足<br />\n但真係要FC，唔好比人帶風向<br />\n開頭係好奇怪既，所以引到大家去查案，引到大家將武力升級<br />\n但同時，黑警就馬上喬裝，四出破壞同放火<br />\n媒體又馬上配合，唱衰你地<br />\n<br />\n老毛：凡是敵人反對的，我們就要擁護；<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">凡是敵人擁護的，我們就要反對。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n敵人開始擁護緊你們既勇武，係時候要小心考慮如何處理"},{"pid":"18e426d6616a05a5181d57338fcb6fd82daa326d","tid":1591666,"uid":72381,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:06:11.000Z","msg":"係咪想我地搞番個環時人民日報不代表我先滿意？<br />\nDLLM呢兩間黨媒日日係度鳩up"},{"pid":"cfccfcfe521a88929f628b4f99fdff837a193504","tid":1591666,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18e426d6616a05a5181d57338fcb6fd82daa326d","tid":1591666,"uid":72381,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:06:11.000Z","msg":"係咪想我地搞番個環時人民日報不代表我先滿意？<br />\nDLLM呢兩間黨媒日日係度鳩up"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:07:22.000Z","msg":"日日諗住作新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" cl